@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@authToken = {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### Login - Obtenir le token
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "camara13fs@gmail.com",
    "password": "admin123"
}

### Register - Créer un nouvel utilisateur (requires admin/superadmin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "user@test.com",
    "password": "Password123!",
    "nom": "Test",
    "prenom": "User",
    "age": 30,
    "role": "user",
    "code_langue": "FR",
    "organisation_id": "1"
}

### Get Profile - Obtenir le profil de l'utilisateur connecté
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Refresh Token - Obtenir un nouveau token d'accès
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "refresh_token": "your_refresh_token_here"
}